item.title: Give VPN a try with ProtonVPN
item.description: If you’re new to VPN services, you can use ProtonVPN’s free plan. The free version allows you to connect to over 20 servers in 3 countries with moderate speeds. ProtonVPN is from the creators of ProtonMail.
